        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>United States-Mexico Electricity Exchange Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to work with the appropriate representatives of the government of Mexico to establish a United States-Mexico Electricity Exchange Initiative that promotes the interconnection of electric transmission facilities between the U.S. southern border states and Mexico.</p>]]>
        </text>
